<div class="app-card-container">
  <div class="card">

        <h1>About Me</h1>

    <hr>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <%= image_tag "Before_after", width: 300, alt: "Profile Image" %> <!-- replace me locally in app/assets/images and name file exact same in ""-->

        <div class="skills">
          <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
            <h4><%= skill.title %></h4>
            <div class="progress">
              <div class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-warning"
              role="progressbar"
              aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized%>"
              aria-valuemax="100"
              style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized%>%"
              ></div>
            </div>

          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>  

      <div class="col-md-8">
        <p>Find me in app/views/pages/about.html.erb overweight to underweight, bullied, broke me, worked in the most degrading jobs to save up for a personal trainer qualification. Approached the Princes Trust about my ambitions to help others do the same. Read my original Reddit Post for a more detailed explination
        What kicked this all off was that i was a victim of bullying because of my size when i was younger. I was fat shamed etc.. It broke me mentally, emotionally and shattered my confidence. 
      </p>

      <p>
        <button
          class="btn btn-primary"
          type="button"
          data-toggle="collapse"
          data-target="#jobHistory"
          aria-expanded="false"
          aria-controler="jobHistory"
        >
          Job History 
        </button>

        <button
          class="btn btn-primary"
          type="button"
          data-toggle="collapse"
          data-target="#education"
          aria-expanded="false"
          aria-controler="education"
        >
          Education 
        </button>
      </p>

      <p>
        <div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
          <div class="card card-block">
            Job 1
          </div>
          <div class="card card-block">
            Job 2
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="collapse" id="education">
          <div class="card card-block">
            school 1
          </div>
          <div class="card card-block">
            school 2
          </div>
        </div>
      </p>

      </div>    
    </div>

  </div>
</div>
